Package: pdfwrm
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Ivaan <dipanshu247k@gmail.com>
Depends: bash, figlet, img2pdf, poppler-utils , gum
Description: PDF watermark remover
 A PDF watermark remover, optimized for image-based PDFs (for example scanned PDF,  NCERT or other digital books).
 It provides a small CLI utility to help remove or reduce visible watermarks from pages.
